TY  - JOUR
TI  - Intransitive Individual Indifference and Transitive Majorities
AU  - Fishburn, Peter C.
AB  - [The results of A. K. Sen and P. K. Pattanaik on sufficient conditions for the transitivity of simple majorities are extended to the case where it is not assumed that the individual's indifference relations are transitive.]
