TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Estimation of Simultaneous Equation Models with Lagged Endogenous Variables and First Order Serially Correlated Errors
AU  - Fair, Ray C.
AB  - [In this paper various methods for the estimation of simultaneous equation models with lagged endogenous variables and first order serially correlated errors are discussed. The methods differ in the number of instrumental variables used. The asymptotic and small sample properties of the various methods are compared, and the variables which must be included as instruments to insure consistent estimates are derived. A suggestion on how to estimate the approximate covariance matrix of the estimators is made.]
